description: TV Asahi Holdings Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, engages in television (TV) broadcasting business in Japan and internationally. The company operates through TV Broadcasting Business, Internet Business, Shopping Business, and Other Businesses. It engages in the time sales, spot sales, program sales, BS/CS, and other sales activities; special programs and sports broadcast activities; and other businesses include internet-related businesses, TV shopping programs, and special events. The company also invests in motion pictures; and sells and leases equipment and DVDs. TV Asahi Holdings Corporation was founded in 1957 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
